website_summaries.verdict: A sturdy and simple end table that's easy to assemble.
pros: This well-built table looks great, and the wood has a nice rustic finish
Stands out for the durable wrought iron legs
Lower wooden shelf comes in handy
24 inches wide by 22 inches deep by 23 inches high

website_summaries.verdict: Gives you the industrial look you want with a few more design accents than others.
pros: Four metal leg posts have a few design accents and a metal X-brace in the back to enhance the overall look of the end table
Nearly perfect height at 23 inches tall
cons: Will want X-brace side against a wall, limiting your layout options

customer_reviews.title: Exceeded my expectations.
customer_reviews.text: The bolts all go through a metal part and into a threaded insert in the wood. All of the holes lined up perfectly. No instructions, but I don't think you can put it together wrong. It all makes sense. It was quite a bit darker than the website pictures, but it is very attractive. It is about the color of my attached pictures.
customer_reviews.author: Logan

customer_reviews.title: Disappointed
customer_reviews.text: I bought this for my husband. The positive - nice toned wood, the top is beautiful, and the size is nice. The negatives, following the directions, putting the screws on to secure the shelves, with just a hand screwdriver, drove the screws thru the wood causing cracks and breakage. Would love to be contacted by the supplier to get new shelves to replace, and we would use shorter screws! Disappointing. I had several other pieces from this manufacturer on my wish list but probably won't take another chance.
customer_reviews.author: MNI

customer_reviews.title: Disappointing
customer_reviews.text: Not what it appears: Only the top shelf measures 26" x 15" The other shelves are 25 1/4" wide by 12" deep When you account for the frames, your usable space is 21" x 12". The shelves are several long slats glued together, not a solid piece. It also means the shelf is not smooth, but uneven.
customer_reviews.author: CK

customer_reviews.title: Nice, heavy easy to put together
customer_reviews.text: I love it. Fiance wasn't too thrilled about the wheels in the picture but now that we have it and it's put together he likes it and sees where wheels are an advantage because this thing is HEAVY. I really love the dimensions of it and how it's on the low side. It goes great with our sectional couch. I have a pic there are some extra dings on mine because I bought it Amazon warehouse and knew that there would be slight damage. That said, it's supposed to be distressed and I saved a bunch of money to have it just slightly more distressed. Easy to put together, I did it myself in about an hour.
customer_reviews.author: Angela_GTop Contributor: Cooking

customer_reviews.title: Really very nice - BUT don't screw the screws in all the way!  They are a little bit too long
customer_reviews.text: This is actually a really nice desk - it is sturdy and looks more expensive than it is. I had read the reviews and knew there was an issue with the screws - and then when it came I didn't put it together for like a month and totally forgot about the reviews and sure enough two of my screws went clear through to the other side. LOL. A little wood putty covered up the holes and I still really like the desk.
customer_reviews.author: Hanna Barbera

customer_reviews.title: These are better than expected!
customer_reviews.text: These were easy to put together (I bought 2) and worth every penny! Arrived on time and in perfect shape! I redesign my home a lot and I have moved them multiple times by myself and are so fun to decorate and used in multiple different room and different purposes! Furniture now a days is made as cheap and flimsy as possible and these are sturdy shelves on thick metal and easily hold heavy planters, glass, etc...
customer_reviews.author: Casia

customer_reviews.title: A fine working desk that exceeded expectations
customer_reviews.text: I was looking for a relatively plain desk, of good size, with minimal ornamentation and no draws. The desk's shelving is of good size and has proved to be a useful feature that I had not originally contemplated. My original ideal benchmark was a simple board on two trestles: this a far better solution and is a definite addition which, because of its open design, does not fill or box-in the room. The desk is of a good working height and has ample workspace. It is of sturdy construction and is a solid piece of furniture. I am very pleased with this purchase.
customer_reviews.author: Gadshill

customer_reviews.title: Good Product, though...
customer_reviews.text: There are two things that went a bit off the plan - One wood panel arrived damaged slightly. The corner is chipped off. The box it arrived in wasn't damaged, just one of the wooden shelves will require work or replacement. Also, both shelves i ordered had missing set of screws. Whoever packed the shelves should pay attention i guess... I would expect the missing parts to be shipped asap. 3.20.13 - The customer service impressed with a solution and reimbursed for the damages and missing parts. Great Service. Thank you.
customer_reviews.author: Alexander

customer_reviews.title: Nice for the price.
customer_reviews.text: Really do like this desk. Nice size, very sturdy. Only two drawbacks I have are: 1) it’s not solid wood. The shelves are cardboard with a veneer. The top is edged by 4” pieces of wood but the main section is the same as the shelves. I left one shelf out to make room for my PC and the dog chewed the shelf. It’s cardboard. Really nicely done though and it would have been really hard to tell it wasn’t solid wood. 2) there are two different length screws. They really should make this more clear as you can damage a shelf if you use the longer ones. Other than that I am very happy and do recommend this desk!
customer_reviews.author: Darrell R.

customer_reviews.title: Surprising quality
customer_reviews.text: Looks great, very "vintage-y" for the price. The color and finish of both wood and metal is very authentic and high-quality. The fit of everything was better than expected, with excellent stability throughout, helped by the very solid weight of the assembled product. The front and back boards on top are a little uneven, at least on my desk, but not enough to interfere with a notebook, laptop, or keyboard. Assembly took more time than I expected, with lots of screw/bolts to assemble and attach, and the top would be heavy for a small person, but complexity was low.
customer_reviews.author: Tom I.

customer_reviews.title: Great in Small Spaces and Good Looking
customer_reviews.text: We purchased this for our laundry room (very small space). It is amazingly sturdy. Easy to assemble. Vintage look is awesome. It holds all of our laundry supplies (detergent, etc.) as well as a few baskets on the upper shelves holding a heavy amount of cookbooks and other items. We are going to be purchasing the larger/wider size for a bookshelf in our hallway.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: May be more rustic than expected
customer_reviews.text: Pros: Size, color, etc. as expected. Seems to be real wood and sturdy. 1 person could assemble, very easy for 2 people to assemble. Cons: Missing 3 washers. Nearly every wooden piece is chipped or scratched. 1 of the main metal support pieces bent and a soldered edge cracked.
customer_reviews.author: C Gear

customer_reviews.title: Nice industrial chic look
customer_reviews.text: This is nicer than I thought. It is simple to put together and if you are using it for books and nothing ridiculously heavy, it is perfectly designed. The mechanism given to secure it to the wall is poorly designed and useless, but it was stable enough that I didn't need it.
customer_reviews.author: Joan S.

customer_reviews.title: Love this, exactly what I wanted
customer_reviews.text: Absolutely love this shelving unit. We purchased it to house various beer growlers that we pick up from craft breweries around the country. The wooden shelves are real wood and of nice quality. The entire piece has a rustic/industrial look which is exactly what I wanted. Went together easily. The hardware provided to anchor the unit to the wall is useless as you can't get the unit close enough to the wall to use it. We will purchase a different L bracket for this purpose.
customer_reviews.author: Kayla

customer_reviews.title: It looks very nice and was very easy to assemble
customer_reviews.text: It looks very nice and was very easy to assemble, but it keep getting new scratches and I have no idea where they are coming from. I don't move the table and never had anything fall on it or bang against it. I think it's just from regular use, putting books on it, moving around the keyboard, etc. So not very well made as I've only had it for a few months and already so much visible wear and tear.
customer_reviews.author: Nini

customer_reviews.title: Excellent purchase
customer_reviews.text: Very pleased with this purchase! I have been searching for a good looking microwave stand and couldn’t find anything I liked. I found this table and it’s perfect for what I need! The table is very attractive and sturdy...made from solid wood and iron. Took only a few minutes to assemble. The only problem is the table looks so nice I think I need a nicer microwave now.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Quality, simple shelf with lots of space.
customer_reviews.text: This shelf is really good quality, easy to put together, and sturdy. It has the wrought iron pillars, with real solid wood shelving (they are heavy, thick wood). It looks really nice in my living room and holds quite a bit of stuff. My only complaint is the "X" attachment in the back is a bit flimsy, and I kind of don't like the metal notches just below the very top shelf...I personally like simple, and I think that made it a little tacky... but I got over it... because overall for the price it's still really pretty, well made, and good quality.
customer_reviews.author: Noneyabusiness

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful! Shelves look like reclaimed wood.
customer_reviews.text: I love this bookcase, it is exactly what I was looking for to match my Industrial decor. The shelves are made of poplar wood which give the look of reclaimed wood. Shelves have a beautiful grain that adds to the look of a more expensive bookcase. I've been looking around at different stores and websites and this was the best looking bookcase for a great price. I only ordered one because for the price I was almost expecting I would be disappointed in the quality but I'm so glad I was wrong. I love it so much, I'm planning on buying another one. I also appreciated how simple it was to put together.
customer_reviews.author: Pandora

customer_reviews.title: Love it!
customer_reviews.text: Love this coffee table! Easy to put the wheels on and looks terrific. Just bought a lake house and this was the perfect fit. Sturdy, beautiful finish and the hardware is really nice. Couldn't be happier!!
customer_reviews.author: KLS

customer_reviews.title: Perfect for Home Office
customer_reviews.text: I've started working from home recently & rigging up on the kitchen table was impractical & cramped, so I bought this desk to expand my home office workspace. The assembly was a breeze; all pieces & hardware were included with nothing missing or damaged & the unit fit together with no issues. It may be a bit pricey, but the materials are very sturdy & attractive, so I believe I made a good choice.
customer_reviews.author: Klaatu Barada Nicto

customer_reviews.title: Love the dimensions, design, and materials.
customer_reviews.text: The pilot holes are a bit too big leaving screws to strip out. Not likely an integrity issue but surprising in a solid wood piece, especially since the screws were hand-driven. Larger, earthquake straps could have been included instead of the zip tie/drywall anchor add on. I know it's more cost but it dramatically increases the security and safety of this device and should be added by anyone buying this.
customer_reviews.author: Portland Dude

customer_reviews.title: Works for our use
customer_reviews.text: We needed a new end table that would fit a medium sized subwoofer under it. We have a SVS PB2000 sub and this fit perfect over the top if we remove bottom shelf. Works well for us to consolidate some space. Wish it were a little taller so its closer to the arm of the couch. The fit and finish isnt ultra high quality and wont will you any awards but it does go together easy and looks decent.
customer_reviews.author: The Enginerd

customer_reviews.title: Finally-it's mine!
customer_reviews.text: This table was on my list of must haves. After 4 years of wanting it I bought it. It arrived on time. Packaging could be a lot better. It arrived unscathed. Easy to put together. You simply add the wheels and axle. I love it. The finish is semi gloss. Heavy casters and wood. Looks really rustic. Luv luv luv.
customer_reviews.author: The Daughter of a King

customer_reviews.title: Solid bargain
customer_reviews.text: The bookcase was exactly what I was expecting. It’s pretty solid and looks nice. I purchased 2 and they are on carpet. If we had children or they were in a high traffic area I would attach them to a wall for safety. The wood is a little darker than it looked online and complement the medium-stained furniture in the office. The shelves are fairly far apart, which makes it challenging to make some of the lower items on the shelves look nice. But considering the price point I’m satisfied.
customer_reviews.author: L. Ware

customer_reviews.title: Real wood!
customer_reviews.text: It was easy to assemble. Made from real wood and is very sturdy. The only ‘negative’ thing is even though the wood looks nice, the reclaimed nature of it means the writing surface is not perfectly smooth. I got a desk pad and now it is a perfect set up.
customer_reviews.author: Crystal

customer_reviews.title: Perfect smaller bookcase
customer_reviews.text: I bought 2 of these units to put on the sides of my TV. My friend had no problem putting them together and they are sturdy. They look super nice and provide much space for special items and books. I may get the TV stand in the future but it looks great with the cabinet I now have. This was definitely a good purchase, the bookshelves are perfect for my living room.
customer_reviews.author: Paris 2B

customer_reviews.title: Top part of metal posts are cracked and will end ...
customer_reviews.text: Top part of metal posts are cracked and will end up falling apart if you mess with it I had put my piece together in hopes it wouldn’t break put it in the corner where I wanted it and leaving it there. I’m too lazy to take it apart or send it back as I noticed this after it was together already.
customer_reviews.author: Giulz

customer_reviews.title: Mind Blowing Beautiful!
customer_reviews.text: I purchased two of these desks. I know they are SOLID WOOD because I drilled 2" holes for routing cords and used the hole covers bought at most office stores. Yes they are smelly. It will go away. But I dare you to buy any tables that are solid wood and this STURDY. The tops are absolutely beautiful, like blow your mind beautiful. I'd buy these again without a doubt. If you're on the fence get off! You won't regret it.
customer_reviews.author: Pastor Steve

customer_reviews.title: Poor quality for the price.
customer_reviews.text: These are very cheap quality for the price. The side "metal" pieces aren't very sturdy and I'm afraid they won't hold much weight on the shelves. I ordered two of these bookcases and one of the metal pieces was broken at the top on arrival and one of the screw holes for the cross in the back was stripped on one of the units. Not worth $160 each. The only reason I'm keeping them is because its way too much work to take them apart and send them back. Overall the appearance is ok. Just wish they were better quality for the price.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Fits in my available space
customer_reviews.text: Beautiful and perfect fit for the spot I wanted it for. It is very sturdy and tall although the tops of the wood shelves are very bumpy/lumpy.
customer_reviews.author: B & V

customer_reviews.title: Looks good, but maybe not the best quality.
customer_reviews.text: The table looks great, but the top has a large crack down the middle and one of the corners is broke off. In fairness, I did buy it in "like new" shape. Perhaps it was broke by the last person who got it. Either way, that kind of damage may indicate quality of item.
customer_reviews.author: Mother of Pearl

customer_reviews.title: Best price for quality
customer_reviews.text: Extremely happy with this purchase. I received the desk yesterday and put it together in less than 30 minutes with a screw gun. I chose this desk because it was all real hardwood pine. Also love the distressed look of the wood. For the price you can’t get a better deal- I searched Overstock and Wayfair and this was a great deal. I also bought the matching bookcase which took 10 min to install. Love them both
customer_reviews.author: Gary T

customer_reviews.title: Finally got them!
customer_reviews.text: I looked all over for this type of self. There was a certain brand ‘Home’ something, can’t remember who makes them,buy higher priced. I found that brand on Amazon and Jet-cheaper there. However, I found this brand and same concept and quality...cheaper. I bought two and it took 30 minutes for both-easy. I would buy again.
customer_reviews.author: Misty

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful desk!
customer_reviews.text: This is a fantastic desk. Nice and solid, real wood (which was important to me), and has a lot of character. It wasn't too hard to put together, though having two people definitely helps. There's lots of space in the shelves, and lots of great surface area. It looks great in my office at home.
customer_reviews.author: Rachel Lovinger

customer_reviews.title: Awesome, sturdy, beautiful shelf... arrived slightly broken
customer_reviews.text: I love the shelves. The wood and metal are beautiful, and the unit feels sturdy. I would buy this again, except for one problem. One of the shelves arrived broken. The outer box seemed fine but a corner was missing from one of the shelves, and I found the missing corner inside the box.
customer_reviews.author: Carrie

customer_reviews.title: Nice simple piece, ships well.
customer_reviews.text: Very attractive shelving. It feels a little cheap when you're putting the shelves in but doesn't show it. Very sturdy materials and great packing for shipping. The delivery guy left it laid across the entrance to my garage and I it it with my car but there was no damage to the actual product. Easy to set up.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: solid shelf at a great price
customer_reviews.text: Solid shelf that looks nice at a great price. Its not steel but light aluminium tubing (still solid). Bump out detail on tube near top is not smooth but rough welded in a few spots only. I wish that part looked better. Wood looks nice and rustic but a bit darker than I thought it would be. Also wood is very light weight...maybe not solid plank? Smelled of heavy chemicals out of box but dissipated quickly. Box was beat to hell on arrival but product was fine. Packing material wasnt the best so maybe I got lucky. Fast shipping and easy assembly. Overall satisfied with the product and would buy again for same price.
customer_reviews.author: John C

customer_reviews.title: Pleasantly surprised!
customer_reviews.text: Very nice piece of furniture at a reasonable price. The wood shelves are of good quality, not compressed pieces. The entire self is very sturdy and was easy to put together. The metal frame isn't too heavy that I can't move the shelf by myself and it also came with felt pieces under the metal legs that keep my wood flooring from getting scuffed. An added bonus, the shelf came with hardware that allows you to anchor the shelf to the wall should you have small children that might want to pull on it. How nifty!
customer_reviews.author: Bex

customer_reviews.title: Nice for the Price!
customer_reviews.text: This bookcase looks great in the den that is short on space. It is a rich, light tobacco color. Well packaged and simple assembly - you only need a Phillips head screwdriver for the metal parts, the shelves have notches on the corners that fit around the metal - too easy. I laid it flat on the floor and assemble alone in about 15 minutes after separating parts. The feet are high enough to clean under and the product, although stable on my floor, also comes with hardware to stabilize to the wall if wanted.
customer_reviews.author: Value and Cost

customer_reviews.title: Love it!
customer_reviews.text: I saw this shelf in the store for over $300, so when I stumbled upon it on Amazon for much less, I got pretty excited. It is beautiful and adds such an industrial feel to the room. The shelf came with all of the pieces and didn't take long to put together. The rods on the back really help with the stability of the shelf. Will definitely keep this piece around for many years to come!
customer_reviews.author: Tylor/Jess

customer_reviews.title: mission style desk
customer_reviews.text: the desk looks nice. the assembly instructions could have been better though. there's no reason the screws had to be different sizes. I only realized they were different when one went through the finish and ruined one of the shelves.
customer_reviews.author: Pam

customer_reviews.title: Stylish
customer_reviews.text: I love the look of these shelves, but we had to create end pieces eg: bookends (1 at each end of each shelf) to keep books from falling off either end. Our solution worked, so I am happy.
customer_reviews.author: Christi B.

customer_reviews.title: Overall good product, cute!
customer_reviews.text: I was pretty impressed with this product. The wood is beautiful and real but the craftsmanship on the metal is questionable. A small welded dot shows where each peice meets on the metal, I have included photos of it. But overall I am satisfied.
customer_reviews.author: C.H.

customer_reviews.title: It looks nice. It went together easily but be careful to ...
customer_reviews.text: This bookshelf fit perfectly with my entertainment center. There is plenty of room between shelves to stack games or books. It looks nice. It went together easily but be careful to have the holes in the sides facing toward the back so that the cross stabilization support an be attached. It was vey sturdy after assembled, but I did secure it to the wall as suggested.
customer_reviews.author: tac1

customer_reviews.title: Great tables!
customer_reviews.text: I really love these! They were extremely easy to put together. I bought two and had them assembled in just a few minutes. The only problem I had was one table was missing a pre-drilled hole for the X in the back so I just left them off of both tables which didn’t bother me. Other than that, they’re great.
customer_reviews.author: Jami J.

customer_reviews.title: Good construction, nice look
customer_reviews.text: I was looking for a desk for around a year and couldnt find one that fit all my requirements. This one checked all my boxes. Its sturdy, looks really nice and was easy to put together. its large enough to fit my computer tower and my two 27 inch monitors. Came in the mail with no damage, all the screw wholes lined up, no damage to the wood top, shelves, or frame. No buyers remorse on this one.
customer_reviews.author: Kenan

customer_reviews.title: These look amazing in my apartment next to brown leather furniture
customer_reviews.text: These look amazing in my apartment next to brown leather furniture. They are sturdy and look far more expensive than they are. I will note that we encountered one defect when putting it together - one of the screw holes was too small and we could not use the screw provided. We improvised with another random screw we had that was a bit smaller. Other than that snag, I am pleasantly surprised with this product.
customer_reviews.author: monique

customer_reviews.title: No instructions but easy assembly.
customer_reviews.text: I bought this for my study to match the desk in the same style. I love the rustic look of it. The only issue I had is that it comes needing assembly and mine did not include instructions. It was pretty simple without them, though.
customer_reviews.author: Jim D.

customer_reviews.title: Love the Furniture.....  Can do a tad better on QA next time.
customer_reviews.text: I love the Home Elegance series of furniture. This is about my 10th or 11th piece. Usually arrive in great shape. This one came with two broken edges (both where the wood wraps around the metal legs) and a dent in the credenza top. I was able to get it together. Chose not to return. Better QA might be needed, as the box was not damaged, so I assume inserted broken at the factory. Hard to say.
customer_reviews.author: Patrick Dawson

customer_reviews.title: I’m almost excited to work more from home!
customer_reviews.text: I finally caved and agreed to a home office. As I live in a loft I needed something that would have storage, fit with the style, fit and of course be functional! This really did meet all the criteria and was under budget.
customer_reviews.author: Jess W

customer_reviews.title: Authentic Chinese rustic, good value.
customer_reviews.text: Good value overall, could easily sell in retail for 2x, if it was American made of good wood 3-4x, but it's not and the quality is typical Chinese. Real wood and somewhat light weight metal, I wouldnt stand on it though. It has a rather authentic rustic quality to it. Packaging was crap, a weld was missing, and the screw holes should be drilled to prevent cracking when assembling. But overall very satisfied for what I paid.
customer_reviews.author: Ray M

customer_reviews.title: It looks great, and it's easy to put together and sturdy
customer_reviews.text: It looks great, and it's easy to put together and sturdy. A few people had asked if it has an odor when first unpacked, some said no, being one of those people who is very sensitive to odors and susceptible to migraines due to them, YES, the off-gassing was terrible. I'd suggest opening the box in an airy space for about 24 hours and then assembling it.
customer_reviews.author: Gwen Urie

customer_reviews.title: This table looks great, and was fairly simple to put together
customer_reviews.text: This table looks great, and was fairly simple to put together. My husband did it himself in under a half hour. The top is slightly rougher than I expected, but lends itself to the rustic look I was going for. I don't use it for drinks as the top is not level in places, but it works for my lamp and knick knacks.
customer_reviews.author: Mrs. H

customer_reviews.title: Please with the product- no surprises
customer_reviews.text: Contrary to other buyers I had no problems at all with my order. All pieces were intact; all holes aligned; and with my electric screwdriver- I put this together in 15 minutes. Finish is good for the price and love the wood shelves and industrial look. This is a narrow shelf- and because of that it is not as stable as it could be. I found that placing heaviest books on the lower bottom shelve improved stability. Besides that- just perfect and at a fair price.
customer_reviews.author: Ben

customer_reviews.title: IN LOVE
customer_reviews.text: Got this today and the desk is amazing really great built and spacious for me. It was really simple to put together.At first I was debating between this desk and the Teagan from World Market, but now seeing this desk in person its definitely a better quality best and better wood than the Teagan from World Market. I also have Prime and this desk shipped free with it so that is another plus. SO if you are a college student trying to find a big desk i would definitely recommend this one.
customer_reviews.author: Gia Nguyen

customer_reviews.title: Attractive, yet functional.
customer_reviews.text: I like the sturdiness of the desk. I'm considering sanding and coating the top, to prevent tiny slivers--it really needs a good clear-coat.
customer_reviews.author: Mrearly

customer_reviews.title: I was completely satisfied with this purchase
customer_reviews.text: I was completely satisfied with this purchase. It was exactly as pictured and described. The shelves are solid wood and have a nice rustic look to them. The assembly was about as easy as it gets. I was a little concerned that it might have been damaged in the shipping process as the box looked really beat up and even had some large tears in it, but it turned out to be fine. You may want to open the actual package outside as they pack it up nice with Styrofoam, but it gets so beat up in the shipping process that if you open it inside, you will have mess of tiny Styrofoam bits to clean up.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Inferior craftsmanship.
customer_reviews.text: After a lot of research I decided on the price of this bookcase. It looks good, fits the space. However, the wood shelves were cut wrong and were "patched" with little squares to fill in the area where they were cut. Its on both sides, so you can't just put them to the back. I would consider this a fairly large issue and would return it if I had not already assembled it and threw the box away.
customer_reviews.author: shellee

customer_reviews.title: Need assistance
customer_reviews.text: Two of boards included are broken. The board labeled "d" is cracked and one of the boards labeled "c" is broken. I would like replacements for the damaged boards only. I cannot ship the rest of the unit back because the packaging has been destroyed and finding a new box to fit everything would be too much work.
customer_reviews.author: William Graber

customer_reviews.title: So easy to assemble!!!
customer_reviews.text: Best piece of furniture I’ve ever bought on line. Mine arrived in perfect condition and took like 10 minutes to assemble. So easy! Looks great in my space. Might buy another one.
customer_reviews.author: fishers, in

customer_reviews.title: I have Two
customer_reviews.text: I love this bookcase, it came well packaged and quick shipping. It's sturdy and perfect for a rustic chic look. I would have liked if the shelves where a bit heavier but overall it's good quality for the price... As long as it doesn't go over $200 :) I originally purchased one and had it for a few months then purchased my second bookcase because it so well with my decor.
customer_reviews.author: Quelinda

customer_reviews.title: Best purchase!
customer_reviews.text: I love this table in my living room. Gets tins of compliments and it looks wonderful. The imperfection are exactly what I was after. Great buy for the price.
customer_reviews.author: YA

customer_reviews.title: Solid desk
customer_reviews.text: Desk is definitely made of wood. The legs could be made of a bit more solid metal to help support the weight of the wood. But, it isn't going anywhere. Nothing I would worry about or deter from a purchase. It is beautiful! I do recommend a workspace cover / mat as it is rough / rustic wood. I love the rustic, yet sleek look. I am getting baskets to put on the shelves to help organize the storage. Love it!!!!
customer_reviews.author: Carol Paasch

customer_reviews.title: Great look, defective product
customer_reviews.text: The bookcase itself is stunning. Very nice quality (black posts), color of the wood (purchased brown color) and it has a wonderful industrial-style look. It received only 3 stars because there were three broken pieces on the bookshelves, that other customers mentioned. With a little wood glue, the problem was rectified. I would also recommend fastening the shelving to the wall to prevent tipping; the base of the bookshelf is not very wide...
customer_reviews.author: MommyM84

customer_reviews.title: Super pleased with this piece and highly recommend
customer_reviews.text: Assembly was so quick and simple - my husband was able to put it together in the time it took me to load the dishwasher after dinner. Seriously. Well built and half the price of the EXACT model I was about to purchase on Target's website, Super pleased with this piece and highly recommend!
customer_reviews.author: S. Arnolt

customer_reviews.title: Very well made.  No complaints!
customer_reviews.text: Very well made and easy to put together. Solid wood and Steel materials Should last a lifetime. Best ONE I've noticed on here.
customer_reviews.author: jonathan

customer_reviews.title: It looks nice but part of its shelf arrived broken.
customer_reviews.text: Bought it because of good reviews. Charming to look at. Fairly easy to assemble. However, one of the shelves is broken. I would like a replacement shelf for that one. It (one of the horizontal shelves) is supposed to connect around the vertical piece in a U shape. But a piece is broken off (see photo). Hopefully I will receive a replacement shelf without hassle and will update this review accordingly if I do.
customer_reviews.author: L

customer_reviews.title: We liked this bookcase so much that we decided to order more
customer_reviews.text: Initially we ordered only one of these shelves. It was for an area of our house where the wall is not wide enough for a standard width bookshelf. We liked the bookcase so much that we decided to order more and place them along our living room wall. They are an open design so bookends are needed but it allows us to be more creative in how the books are displayed.
customer_reviews.author: Mythral

customer_reviews.title: The bookcase looks great and really fits in with the industrial vibe I ...
customer_reviews.text: The bookcase looks great and really fits in with the industrial vibe I wanted, but one of the middle shelves came broken (the little wooden nook bit that goes right next to the poles) and another broke on installation. I managed to conceal both without affecting the integrity of the case, but I'm a little disappointed in the workmanship.
customer_reviews.author: nimm45

customer_reviews.title: Nice real wood shelf
customer_reviews.text: This shelf is working out great. Needed this size for a certain corner in our living room. It was very easy to assemble and is very sturdy (although we're just putting some pictures and knick-knacks on it)
customer_reviews.author: Customer

customer_reviews.title: Sturdy, beautiful
customer_reviews.text: We love this! It fits our extremely narrow corner space perfectly, looks way better than the price would suggest, and was fairly easy to put together. Probably enough room for 100 books.
customer_reviews.author: A Grey

customer_reviews.title: Attractive Bookshelf
customer_reviews.text: Attractive looking bookshelves, all wood. A few things that didn't make me give it a 5 star. One of the iron sidings was compromised. Looks like the painting or protective layer was damaged by heat and bubbled a bit then hardened. One other thing is the bottom shelf had damage on the corner. I would have liked the wood to sit more plush against the iron but the weight of books keeps the wood stabilized. Easy assembly, took about 30 minutes. I'm a perfectionist so it took me a longer since I wanted to get everything aligned.
customer_reviews.author: Annette Elguea

customer_reviews.title: Arrived broken
customer_reviews.text: We purchased the same shelving unit 2 years ago and loved it! Decided to buy a second one. But unfortunately the second one arrived broken with the package of screws open/screws missing. Big disappointment and annoying to return.
customer_reviews.author: Megan Hughes

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful - but received damaged item
customer_reviews.text: These are generally high quality bookshelves but unfortunately we received a very bent side metal bar. We would love to receive a new side bar if possible (please see photos). If it weren’t for the damaged product I would say I love these shelves!
customer_reviews.author: Catherine Cheek

customer_reviews.title: Love them!
customer_reviews.text: Beautiful addition to my home. I love the two that I purchased! I have added a photo that I took not long after I assembled them (with the help of a friend). I stongly advise using the provided all anchors!
customer_reviews.author: Amanda

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful And Affordable
customer_reviews.text: I purchased 2 of these beauties. My husband assembled them both in under an hour! (Plus, he says he was a little distracted by the Ellen DeGeneres Show, hehehe, so it could have taken less time!) These shelves are pretty and stable and have just the industrial look I have been searching for without being overpriced. They arrived on time and without blemish. As stated in reviews I read, they do have a very strong varnish smell that dissipates in about 24 hours so if you have sensitivities to smells, let them air out on a porch or in your garage if you can.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Excellent product
customer_reviews.text: Excellent product. Extremely easy to assemble. Like other reviews the finish is darker than pictured and it does have natural wood grooves. Fast shipping. LOVE IT.
customer_reviews.author: B. Truninger

customer_reviews.title: Love this shelving unit
customer_reviews.text: Love this shelving unit. The only issue I have with it is that there were no holes drilled through the metal frame for which to attach the bottom shelf to the frame, on one side. I did not feel like trying to drill these holes myself, so I just left the bottom shelf unattached on the one side. It seems sturdy enough, but will have to remember that the bottom shelf is not attached when moving the unit.
customer_reviews.author: S. Revels

customer_reviews.title: Very easy to put together and looks great
customer_reviews.text: Very easy to put together and looks great. I was concerned it would be wobbly like ikea furniture, but it is very sturdy and holds all our glassware perfectly. It did come with a slight defect in that the wood was broken by the notch where the leg was suppose to fit, but we had wood glue handy so didn't worry about it. Once the glue dried you can't even see the crack
customer_reviews.author: Lee G.

customer_reviews.title: Gorgeous solid wood desk!
customer_reviews.text: This is an amazing beautiful desk. I really didn’t know what to expect. It’s very stylish and would go with so many decor styles. It’s hard to find solid wood pieces anymore. It’s very sturdy and well made. Make sure you pay attention to the screws size when you assemble it and use it in the proper place.
customer_reviews.author: JM

customer_reviews.title: Very cool coffee table
customer_reviews.text: This table completes my living room. It’s very heavy as the wheels are made of real iron😬 No complaints here!
customer_reviews.author: CaliCapriSun

customer_reviews.title: Good Luck!
customer_reviews.text: Bought the same brand of matching end tables & a book shelf with desk they were without damage. But when I open the last piece of low shelving the slots that the shelves rest on were almost broken off on both shelves, the packing was damages, I had already cut up the box before unwrapping the shelves. Had to glue them and are waiting to see if they hold up. Other wise I'm going to try and return it. Good Luck !
customer_reviews.author: Jeff Simon

customer_reviews.title: They are sturdy and look great in our apartment
customer_reviews.text: Assembly took a little while, but we get complements on these all of the time. They are sturdy and look great in our apartment. The wood is a warm, brown..not light but not dark.
customer_reviews.author: Christian Maynes

customer_reviews.title: Looks great and the quality is excellent
customer_reviews.text: Looks great, solid wood. Was easy to put together. Very durable and a good size shelf to store many items on. if you like the style they also have other furniture that you can purchase that go well together.
customer_reviews.author: Ken

customer_reviews.title: Value-priced, at a slight cost
customer_reviews.text: This shelf is one of the cheaper of its kind out there, so it is a good buy as far as price is concerned. From a distance this shelf looks great and you would not be able to tell it is on the lower side of the cost spectrum. But once you get up closer you'll notice that the wood shelf layers are a little warped, that some of the metal welding is not perfect, and that the shelf definitely has a made-in-china smell. It's a little wobbly even when assembled, too, but that doesn't take away from its visual appeal when it's just sitting there in the room.
customer_reviews.author: PeterP

customer_reviews.title: Love it so much, we bought a 2nd
customer_reviews.text: We bought one some time ago and then my son liked it so much we bought one for him. It has plenty of surface space for monitors, keyboard, mouse, joystick and other junk. The shelves are big enough for gaming consoles, organizing bins and misc peripherals. It's sturdy and strong and looks great with a weathered/industrial look.
customer_reviews.author: Carrie

customer_reviews.title: Very poor quality control.
customer_reviews.text: Threaded inserts to attach table top to legs are missing, not just 1 or 2, all of them. This is very obvious, and should have been seen before boxing and shipping. To large of an item to re-box and send back. I will fix myself. Very disappointing.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Very nice piece!
customer_reviews.text: This turned out to be exactly what I needed to complete an area in my home that could hold different items. It was very easy to put together & took no time at all. One of the shelves had the edge notch area broken off. I was able to wood glue it back & it looks fine.
customer_reviews.author: BarbG

customer_reviews.title: 👍🏻
customer_reviews.text: Very easy to put together! Made of real wood and iron/ metal. Love the shelf space and tall 6 ft.
customer_reviews.author: DA

customer_reviews.title: Easy to Assemble and Good Quality
customer_reviews.text: Was easy to put together. I chose a simple desk as I've struggled with excessive parts and poor instructions in the past. This desk has solid wood and a distressed look. As part of a collection, I can add bookcases that match. The only problem was a dent on the center edge but as it's already distressed wood, it's fixed with wood coloring and a bit of rough sandpaper.
customer_reviews.author: RIchard Clark

customer_reviews.title: Damaged/Missing parts
customer_reviews.text: Lets see if amazon removed this review like my other 2. This looks good but item came broken. Two shelves were damaged and no hardware. Third item from amazon missing parts and broken. They forgot about the quality over quantity.
customer_reviews.author: chris vanacore

customer_reviews.title: Decent for the price
customer_reviews.text: This is a nice looking bookshelf for the price but I can only give it 3 stars because a portion of the bottom shelf broke (thank goodness I have wood glue at home and know how to use it) and the metal portion is very light. I thought it would be heavier. My suggestion to the manufacturer of this product is to not make the shelves so thin
customer_reviews.author: mcamfrancis

customer_reviews.title: Love these bookshelves!
customer_reviews.text: Love, love, looove these bookshelves. I bought two and they are fairly easy to put together except for the back metal "x" part...still not sure if I did that right. Even though I failed at the last part of the assembly, they still look good and feel pretty sturdy. On a side note, I can't assemble anything so if I could put these together ANYONE can (took about an hour total for both - 45 minutes to figure out the first one and 15 minutes for the second one).
customer_reviews.author: Cassandra C.

customer_reviews.title: Love 'em!
customer_reviews.text: I ended up buying two of these, one after the other, because I liked the first one so much. Neither had any damages. The second one had mis-aligned screw holes on the bottom shelf to attach it to the metal bars along the bottom - so my husband just made new holes himself.
customer_reviews.author: Shannon

customer_reviews.title: Great looking end table!
customer_reviews.text: Nice looking product easy to put together. Concerned about long term durability as the screws do not go very deep into the wood.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: LOVE LOVE LOVE this desk
customer_reviews.text: LOVE LOVE LOVE this desk. Exactly what I was looking for-- a desk that is both wide and long enough to do some hard core studying. The only issue I have was that on of the legs arrived a bit dinged. Nothing too noticeable though.
customer_reviews.author: Caroline Barnhart

customer_reviews.title: Looks good as an industrial piece without spending a ton of ...
customer_reviews.text: Looks good as an industrial piece without spending a ton of cash on this current trend. As expected for price point. First ones were broken, return immediate and easy. Great customer service.
customer_reviews.author: Medical provider

customer_reviews.title: super easy to install
customer_reviews.text: As other reviewers have mentioned, super easy to install. For the price, you really can't beat the look and feel. We bought 3 of these. One of them was having issues with the crossbar in back, the screw would only go in half way. But there is nothing like this at $160 price point.
customer_reviews.author: Barty Mcgee

customer_reviews.title: Strong table that looks good
customer_reviews.text: Perfect size, looks good. Easy to put together. Comes packaged well but you may still encounter a ding here and there. But better then most packaging you find with large furniture.
customer_reviews.author: Ken

customer_reviews.title: Broken Shelves
customer_reviews.text: This is the second bookcase I’ve ordered. However, the shelves arrived damaged, as five wooden “notches” were sheered off. I’m attempting to superglue this, rather than returning, but buyer beware!
customer_reviews.author: LK
